Paper: hep-th/9212111

Date: 1992-12-18

Title: $E_7$ as $D=10$ space-time symmetry --- Origin of the twistor transform

Authors: Martin Cederwall

Comments: 4 pages

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B302 (1993) 189-190

Massless particle dynamics in $D=10$ Minkowski space is given an$E_7$-covariant formulation, including both space-time and twistor variables.$E_7$ contains the conformal algebra as a subalgebra. Analogous constructionsapply to $D=3,4$ and 6.